description:
As the believers pondered the exact meaning of the Bible passages that had led them to the Great Disappointment they restudied and came to a new breath taking conclusion. Christ wasnt going to come back to earth but His ministry would continue in heaven but in a new capacity - in the Holy of Holies! What would this mean and where was that?
